CREATE TABLE derived_ev_sales AS
SELECT
  e.region AS country,
  e.parameter,
  e.powertrain,
  e.year,
  e.value
FROM

WHERE
  e.year >= 2010 AND e.year <= 2018
  AND e.parameter = 'EV sales'
  AND e.region IN ('United Kingdom', 'USA', 'Poland', 'Switzerland', 'Sweden', 'Spain');

CREATE TABLE sustainability AS
SELECT
    g.entity, 
    g.electricity_from_hydro, 
    g.electricity_from_solar,
    g.electricity_from_wind,
    g.electricity_from_other_renewables,
    e.parameter,
    e.powertrain,

%jdbc(hive)
CREATE TABLE merged_tbl AS
SELECT
    e.country,
    e.co2_emission,
    e.electricity_from_coal,
    e.electricity_from_gas,
    e.electricity_from_oil,
    e.electricity_from_nuclear,
    g.electricity_from_hydro,
    g.electricity_from_solar,
    g.electricity_from_wind,
    g.electricity_from_other_renewables,
    g.parameter as sales_type,
    g.powertrain as car_type,
    g.year,
    g.value as qty_sold
FROM
    sustainability g
JOIN 
    climate_change e ON g.entity = e.country;

%jdbc(hive)
-- Carbon intensity of electricity generation from each source of electricity production
SELECT
  country,
  year,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_coal) AS coal_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_wind) AS wind_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_gas) AS gas_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_oil) AS oil_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_hydro) AS hydro_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_solar) AS solar_carbon_intensity,
  MAX(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_other_renewables) AS other_renewables_carbon_intensity
FROM
  merged_tbl e
GROUP BY
  country, year;

%jdbc(hive)
-- Total Carbon intensity of electricity generation from each source of electricity production
SELECT
  country,
  year,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_coal) AS total_coal_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_wind) AS total_wind_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_gas) AS total_gas_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_oil) AS total_oil_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_hydro) AS total_hydro_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_solar) AS total_solar_carbon_intensity,
  SUM(e.co2_emission / e.electricity_from_other_renewables) AS total_other_renewables_carbon_intensity
FROM
  merged_tbl e
GROUP BY
  country, year;

%jdbc(hive)
CREATE TABLE merged_tbl_final AS
SELECT
    m.country,
    m.co2_emission,
    m.sales_type as car_sales_type,
    m.car_type,
    m.year,
    m.qty_sold,
    SUM(m.electricity_from_coal + m.electricity_from_wind + m.electricity_from_gas + m.electricity_from_oil + m.electricity_from_hydro + m.electricity_from_solar + m.electricity_from_other_renewables) AS total_electricity
FROM
  merged_tbl m
WHERE
  m.year >= 2010 AND m.year <= 2018
  AND m.country IN ('United Kingdom', 'United States', 'Poland', 'Switzerland', 'Sweden', 'Spain')
GROUP BY
  m.country, m.co2_emission, m.sales_type, m.car_type, m.year, m.qty_sold;

%jdbc(hive)
-- Plot the co2 emission aginst electricity production accross all six countries over year 2010 to 2018
SELECT DISTINCT country, co2_emission, total_electricity, year from merged_tbl_final

%jdbc(hive)
-- Carbon intensity of electricity generation
SELECT
  m.country,
  m.year,
  m.co2_emission / m.total_electricity AS carbon_intensity
FROM
  (SELECT
    country,
    year,
    SUM(co2_emission) AS co2_emission,
    SUM(total_electricity) AS total_electricity
  FROM
    merged_tbl_final
  GROUP BY
    country, year) m;

%jdbc(hive)
-- Carbon intensity of electricity generation
SELECT country, co2_emission, total_electricity, year from merged_tbl_final where country = 'Poland'

%jdbc(hive)
-- Carbon intensity of electricity generation
SELECT country, co2_emission, total_electricity, year from merged_tbl_final where country = 'United Kingdom'

%jdbc(hive)
describe merged_tbl_final
